{"tid":1930102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【黑警撞車】黑警駕七人車載4男同黨　撞向小巴釀9名市民受傷","createTime":"2020-03-17T10:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T13:04:30.000Z","uid":293677,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"276ba99b58cb86d50a40eda742d53967141ffc36","tid":1930102,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:34:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">發動襲擊的意圖及動機未明，相信事件背後經過精心策劃。<br />\n至今相關組織&quot;忠誠勇毅&quot;仍未對襲擊事件公開承認責任。</span><br />\n<br />\n________________________________________<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WvtU8VD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWvtU8VD.jpg&h=f4778b16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日（17日）早上7時許，一輛小巴沿禾葵里向葵涌道方向行駛，一輛七人車沿葵涌道轉入禾葵里，當兩車駛至禾葵里及葵涌道交界時，七人車懷疑失控撞向小巴，意外中除了七人車女司機受輕傷，另有8人受傷，包括4名七人車乘客及4名小巴乘客。消防員到場營救，傷者全部輕傷由救護車送院。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">肇事七人車由休班女警駕駛，並載着4名休班男警員，他們均駐守油麻地警署。涉事七人車的車尾玻璃，貼有一個寫有<ins>「意見接受、態度照舊」</ins>的牌。</span></span>據車輛登記資料顯示，女車主為一名姓張女子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/448618/%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%92%9E%E8%BB%8A-%E5%A5%B3%E8%AD%A6%E9%A7%95%E4%B8%83%E4%BA%BA%E8%BB%8A%E8%BC%894%E7%94%B7%E5%90%8C%E8%A2%8D-%E5%A4%B1%E6%8E%A7%E6%92%9E%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4%E9%87%809%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F448618%2F%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2592%259E%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%25A7%2595%25E4%25B8%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25BC%25894%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%25A2%258D-%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2592%259E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%2587%25809%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2582%25B7&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzBxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=fa137c77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/448618/%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%92%